name: Infaweb
overview:
Infaweb provide a high quality online marketing and development service to all types of websites.

Jon Harrison, the company MD, is a search engine optimisation (SEO) specialist with detailed knowledge around onsite and offsite SEO.

The company offers a full online service so that any client can get everything they need from one location. Infaweb use a range of companies that it partners with to ensure it can deliver top class services for every aspect of online marketing and development.

From Internet marketing, SEO, Design, Development to mobile platforms. Infaweb have the skill resources to develop the projects you need, making sure they fit your marketing goals and objectives.

Their PPC and SEO expert can guide you through Google while at the same time make sure the developer is creating a solution Google will want to index and rank well.
